5. Appendices
Root Node - First node created for the mind map. Origin of all other nodes.
Parent Node - The creator of a child node.
Child Node - A subordinate node created by the parent node
Plugins - Additional features or extensions that can be added to Freeplane
The document contains details for scripting. For more advanced manipulation of the software. https://docs.freeplane.org/scripting/Start_Here.html. 

